# == Class: glassfish::install
#
# This class manages glassfish installation.
# Can only be called from glassfish::init class.
#
# === Parameters
#
#  None
#
# === Examples
#
# Not applicable
#
# === Authors
#
# Gavin Williams <fatmcgav@gmail.com>
#
# === Copyright
#
